{"id": "3927", "post": "<div class=\"post-3927 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-virtual-servers tag-buffalo tag-new-york tag-openvz tag-servermania-com\" id=\"post-3927\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/servermania-7-month-or-48year-1024mb-openvz-vps-in-buffalo-new-york/\" rel=\"bookmark\">ServerMania \u2013 $7 Month or $48/Year 1024MB OpenVZ VPS in Buffalo, New York</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" data-src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" alt=\"Tags: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/buffalo/\" rel=\"tag\">buffalo</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/new-york/\" rel=\"tag\">new york</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/openvz/\" rel=\"tag\">openvz</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/servermania-com/\" rel=\"tag\">servermania.com</a> <img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" alt=\"Date/Time: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> May 13, 2013 @ 8:05 pm, by Liam</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><p><a href=\"http://www.servermania.com\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/servermania.jpg.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"screenshot litespeed-loaded\" title=\"ServerMania\" alt=\"\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/servermania.jpg.webp\" width=\"300\" height=\"190\" data-was-processed=\"true\"></a>Kevin, from <a href=\"http://www.servermania.com\">ServerMania</a>, has sent in his second LowEndBox OpenVZ offer which is available in Buffalo, New York.</p><table><tbody><tr><td valign=\"top\"><strong>VPS-1024L Plan</strong><p></p><ul><li>1024MB RAM</li><li>2048MB Burst</li><li>75 GB RAID10 Diskspace</li><li>2000GB Bandwidth</li><li>100Mbit Port</li><li>1 IPv4 Address</li><li>OpenVZ/SolusVM</li><li>$7/Month | <a href=\"https://shp.servermania.com/order/product?p=532\">Order Link</a></li><li>$17.85/Quarter | <a href=\"https://shp.servermania.com/order/product?p=532&amp;period=3\">Order Link</a></li><li>$29.82/Semi-Annual | <a href=\"https://shp.servermania.com/order/product?p=532&amp;period=6\">Order Link</a></li><li>$47.88/Year | <a href=\"https://shp.servermania.com/order/product?p=532&amp;period=12\">Order Link</a></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table><p>ServerMania were previously known as B2Net Solutions. They operated under this brand for 10 years but they recently underwent rebranding to ServerMania. Interestingly enough, their IP space is still registered as \u201cB2Net Solutions\u201d and the company is legally registered in Ontario, Canada. I\u2019ve noticed ServerMania are utilizing a pretty cool custom billing and order panel which looks great and functions well. ServerMania\u2019s <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/servermania-7-month-1024mb-xenonapp-server-in-buffalo-new-york/\">last offer</a> received many positive comments, reinforcing their \u201cSuperior Support Fleet\u201d motto.<br>\n<span id=\"more-3927\"></span><br>\nServerMania accept payments via Visa, Mastercard and PayPal. They offer a 100% network uptime guarantee and a 100% power uptime guarantee. From my experience, most providers usually offer one or the other, so it\u2019s nice to see both 100% for both! Additional IPv4 addresses are charged at $3/Month. They do not offer any money back guarantee or refunds. As usual, have a read of their <a href=\"http://www.servermania.com/tos.htm\">Terms of Service</a> before signing up.</p><p><strong>Network Information:</strong></p><p>Servers are located at the popular ColoCrossing datacenter in Buffalo, NY.</p><p>Test IPv4:&nbsp;192.157.59.250<br>\nTest File: <a href=\"http://192.157.59.250/100mb.img\">100 MB</a> | <a href=\"http://192.157.59.250/250mb.img\">250MB</a> | <a href=\"http://192.157.59.250/500mb.img\">500MB</a> | <a href=\"http://192.157.59.250/1gb.img\">1GB</a></p><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shape-rounded dpsp-column-auto dpsp-has-spacing dpsp-no-labels dpsp-show-on-mobile dpsp-button-style-1 dpsp-has-icon-background dpsp-has-button-background dpsp-show-total-share-count dpsp-show-total-share-count-after\"><ul class=\"dpsp-networks-btns-wrapper dpsp-networks-btns-content dpsp-has-button-icon-animation\"><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fservermania-7-month-or-48year-1024mb-openvz-vps-in-buffalo-new-york%2F&amp;t=ServerMania%20-%20%247%20Month%20or%20%2448%2FYear%201024MB%20OpenVZ%20VPS%20in%20Buffalo%2C%20New%20York\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-facebook dpsp-no-label dpsp-first\" title=\"Share on Facebook\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=ServerMania%20-%20%247%20Month%20or%20%2448%2FYear%201024MB%20OpenVZ%20VPS%20in%20Buffalo%2C%20New%20York&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fservermania-7-month-or-48year-1024mb-openvz-vps-in-buffalo-new-york%2F&amp;via=LowEndNetwork\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-twitter dpsp-no-label\" title=\"Share on Twitter\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?url=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fservermania-7-month-or-48year-1024mb-openvz-vps-in-buffalo-new-york%2F&amp;title=ServerMania%20-%20%247%20Month%20or%20%2448%2FYear%201024MB%20OpenVZ%20VPS%20in%20Buffalo%2C%20New%20York&amp;mini=true\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-linkedin dpsp-no-label dpsp-last\" title=\"Share on LinkedIn\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li></ul><div class=\"dpsp-tota